pageContext.claim: “The stock market is up. I guess now we're over 30 percent since the election.”
pageContext.analysis: All the markets are up, but Trump doesn't specify to which is referring. The Dow Jones is up 28 percent, the NASDAQ is up 33 percent, while the S&P 500 is up 19 percent. Only the NASDAQ is over 30 percent since election day, which includes the last three months of Obama's presidency.
